Storage needs more defence from user modifications
As the main entry point to the program, extra safety considerations must
be taken into account especially null safety.
We must prevent the event of null elements from occuring within the
program.
As such storage will check that all inputs read from the json file MUST
not contain any null elements.
This acts as a layer one of frontline defence towards null exceptions
from occuring within the program.
